  "content": ";&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"output\">Reload complete.</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>The whole point: absorb the complexity so switching backends is one command, no restart, no config files.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">07 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 8: TAKEAWAYS -->\n<div class=\"slide\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f172a 0%, #1a2332 50%, #0f172a 100%);\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Key Takeaways</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 48px;\">\n    What I Learned<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-green\">From These Numbers</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128200;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">In RAG, retrieval matters more than the model.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">89% of pipeline time was search + graph — not inference. Optimize the retrieval layer first.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#9889;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Shared memory beats raw compute for small models.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">If data transfer costs more than the computation, zero-copy wins.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>",
